ntent/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbijn-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbijn-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbijn-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/David-Gilmour.-Credit-Anton-Corbijn-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/David-Gilmour">大卫·吉尔摩 (David Gilmour)</a>宣布推出“Luck And Strange”，这是他九年来的第一张个人专辑，而该唱片的首张专辑将于本周晚些时候发行。</p><p>这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink-floyd">Pink Floyd</a>吉他手将于周四（4 月 25 日）在 BBC 广播 2 台早餐秀上发行专辑的主打单曲“The Piper&#39;s Call”。该曲目的随附音乐视频将于周五（4 月 26 日）发布。</p><p> 《Luck and Strange》将于 9 月 6 日发行。这张密纹唱片在布莱顿和伦敦录制了五个多月。他的妻子、作家兼作词家波莉·桑普森 (Polly Sampson) <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-floyds-david-gilmour-working-on-new-album-in-the-studio-3562936">此前曾记录过吉尔莫参观工作室的经历，并</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-floyds-david-gilmour-working-on-new-album-in-the-studio-3562936">在她的个人 Instagram 上分享了这些照片</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C589fPFKKcb/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; wid